                "description": "This response is shows that the address-recognition API was able to recognize all the address entities in the text.  Notice that the \`country_code\` and \`address_residential_indicator\` fields are populated with the values that were provided in the request.
",
                "value": {
                  "address": {
                    "address_line1": "3800 North Lamar",
                    "address_line2": "Suite 200",
                    "address_residential_indicator": "yes",
                    "city_locality": "Austin",
                    "country_code": "US",
                    "name": "Margie McMiller",
                    "postal_code": 78652,
                    "state_province": "TX",
                  },
